            <strong class="uppercase">WE ARE NOT LIABLE FOR ANY USAGE, MISUSE, OR CONSEQUENCES OF YOUR USE OF THE SERVICE.</strong> You agree to indemnify, defend, and hold harmless Helpmaton and its affiliates from any claims, damages, losses, liabilities, and expenses (including legal fees) arising from your use of the Service or violation of these Terms.
