            <strong class="uppercase">IMPORTANT - BILLING AND PROVIDER CHARGES:</strong>
          </p>
          <p class="mb-4 text-sm text-neutral-600">
            <strong>Helpmaton Subscription vs. AI Provider Costs:</strong> Your Helpmaton subscription covers platform services only (hosting, agent configuration, workspaces, teams, document search, and Helpmaton API calls). <strong>AI provider calls (such as OpenAI, Anthropic, etc.) are NOT included</strong> in your subscription and are billed separately.
          </p>
          <p class="mb-4 text-sm text-neutral-600">
            <strong>Payment Options for AI Provider Calls:</strong> You have two options for handling AI provider costs:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4 text-sm opacity-90 mb-4">
            <li><strong>Use Your Own API Keys:</strong> You may provide your own API keys from AI providers. In this case, you pay the AI provider directly according to their pricing and terms.</li>
            <li><strong>Purchase Credits:</strong> You may purchase credits through Helpmaton to add to your workspace. These credits are used for AI provider calls and are separate from your platform subscription.</li>
          </ul>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4 text-sm text-neutral-600">
            <li>The Service may integrate with third-party providers, including AI service providers, cloud computing services, and other external services</li>
            <li>You are solely responsible for all charges, fees, bills, and costs incurred from third-party providers</li>
            <li>We are not responsible for any billing disputes, charges, or fees from third-party providers</li>
            <li>You agree to pay all charges directly to third-party providers as required by their terms</li>
            <li>We are not liable for any unexpected charges, overages, or billing issues from third-party providers</li>
