            <strong class="uppercase">WE ARE NOT RESPONSIBLE FOR ANY BILLS, CHARGES, OR FEES FROM PROVIDERS.</strong> Any disputes regarding billing must be resolved directly with the respective third-party provider.
          </p>
        </section>

