            <li>Your use or inability to use the Service</li>
            <li>Any conduct or content of third parties on the Service</li>
            <li>Any unauthorized access to or use of our servers</li>
            <li>Any interruption or cessation of transmission to or from the Service</li>
            <li>Any bugs, viruses, or other harmful code</li>
            <li>Any errors or omissions in any content</li>
            <li>Any loss or damage incurred as a result of your use of the Service</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-soft p-6 mb-6 border border-neutral-200">
