        <section class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-soft p-6 mb-6 border border-neutral-200">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-4">15. CONTACT INFORMATION</h2>
          <p class="mb-4 text-sm text-neutral-600">
            If you have any questions about these Terms of Service, please contact us at:
